oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: McDowell Carnival parade
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of five unidentified people riding in a car in the McDowell Carnival parade. A sign on the side of the car reads "Wonderful things to eat tonight, McDowell Carnival." Another unidentified woman can be seen sitting in a car in the background.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
